<li><a href="http://www.efg2.com/Lab/Graphics/Colors/Chromaticity.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.efg2.com/Lab/Graphics/Colors/Chromaticity.htm" rel="nofollow">efg's Color Chromaticity Diagrams Lab Report</a> and <a href="http://www.efg2.com/Lab/Graphics/Colors/Chromaticity.ZIP" class="external text" title="http://www.efg2.com/Lab/Graphics/Colors/Chromaticity.ZIP" rel="nofollow">Delphi source</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.fho-emden.de/~hoffmann/ciexyz29082000.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.fho-emden.de/~hoffmann/ciexyz29082000.pdf" rel="nofollow">CIE Color Space</a>, Gernot Hoffman</li>
<li><a href="http://cvrl.ioo.ucl.ac.uk/index.htm" class="external text" title="http://cvrl.ioo.ucl.ac.uk/index.htm" rel="nofollow">Annotated downloadable data tables</a>, Andrew Stockman and Lindsay T. Sharpe.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cis.rit.edu/mcsl/research/1931.php" class="external text" title="http://www.cis.rit.edu/mcsl/research/1931.php" rel="nofollow">Calculation from the original experimental data of the CIE 1931 RGB standard observer spectral chromaticity co-ordinates and color matching functions</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.cis.rit.edu/mcsl/online/cie.php" class="external text" title="http://www.cis.rit.edu/mcsl/online/cie.php" rel="nofollow">Colorimetric data useful for calculation</a>, in various file formats</li>
</ul>
